import React from 'react'
import Home from '../pages/Home.jsx'
import {Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import MovieDetail from '../pages/detail/MovieDetail.jsx'
import AllMovie from '../components/AllMovie/AllMovie.jsx'
const Content = () => {
  return (
    <Routes >
        <Route path = '/' element = {<Home/>}/>
        <Route path = '/:category/:id' element = {<MovieDetail/>}></Route>
        <Route path = '/:category' element = {<AllMovie/>}></Route>
        <Route path = '/:category/search/:query' element = {<AllMovie/>}></Route>
    </Routes>
  )
}

export default Content
